    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not just about being tired. i see them at dinner, or when they come over... they look so drained. like they're just checking boxes for me instead of actually wanting to be here. i've always been the one taking care of people, and now it's like i'm just this weight they have to carry around every day. it feels so selfish to keep going like this.",
